### 1. Admin: Dashboard Summary
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2. Admin: List All Orders (Paginated)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/orders?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3. Admin: List All Couriers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/couriers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4. Admin: Block/Unblock Courier
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/couriers/{{courierId}}/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
